her creature.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.DEeTPGEcAUU29gXe]{Predict Foe}&nbsp;</strong>As a reaction, shout a warning to an ally and grant that ally concealment against an attack.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.P914huUKtKXr2zDB]{Reject Augmentation}&nbsp;</strong>Targeted creature is @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.ZacF0l6IwqBwToTJ]{Sickened} and can't use any augmentations for the duration.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.wMBxnYkNbzWJklIB]{Remove Condition}</strong>&nbsp;Remove one moderate harmful condition affecting a creature.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.svfCmxHfEGE6wAMc]{Resist Radiation}&nbsp;</strong>Automatically succeed at saving throws against weak radiation and suppress radiation sickness.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.yd5mQwImyuqd8wUs]{Restoration, Lesser}</strong>&nbsp;Dispel magical ability penalty or cure 1d4 ability damage.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.5aW793TGgd3Kd4Fe]{See Invisibility}</strong>&nbsp;See invisible creatures or objects.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.qbeQtgCtP8avY2ny]{Shield Other}</strong>&nbsp;You take half of the target's Hit Point damage.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.ZsRv2Vcl2iamrcCt]{Song Of The Cosmos}&nbsp;</strong>Creatures near you must succeed at a Will saving throw or be @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.7PPRS6krnvaTHbxh]{Fascinated} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.jA6eTWFaULIpjXAx]{Spider Climb}</strong>&nbsp;Grant ability to walk on walls and ceilings.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.Mn5F4th3ctW5oKJ4]{Status}</strong>&nbsp;Monitor condition and position of allies.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.rJ0acpj21GDJYaim]{Summon Creature}&nbsp;</strong>This spell summons an extraplanar creature.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.GQeKJki7ErOP4qUi]{Venomous Weapon}&nbsp;</strong>You touch a weapon that deals bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage and imbue it with poison.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sf