 planets.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.js1J5j0RAIpMaVOM]{Invisibility, Mass}</strong>&nbsp;Multiple targets are invisible for 1 minute per level or until one target attacks or moves away from other targets affected by spell.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.FUJiXbrtJSqQK9JO]{Planar Barrier}</strong>&nbsp;Seal an area against all planar travel into or within it.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.zNSqMd0Tq5JY8hwQ]{Planar Binding}</strong>&nbsp;Trap an extraplanar creature of CR 10 or lower until it performs a task.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.yjClpQv6CCrRE4EC]{Plane Shift}</strong>&nbsp;As many as eight creatures travel to another plane you choose.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.gNgdSyi4pXQmasmc]{Polymorph}&nbsp;</strong>Change the target's shape into that of another creature.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.w3vQYdl7EZGecOHT]{Polymorph, Mass}&nbsp;</strong>Change multiple target's shapes to that of another creature.</p>\n<p><strong>Resistant Armor, Greater:</strong> Grant DR 15/&mdash; or energy resistance 15 against four energy types.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.o78PjAYBWQpiHwMK]{Shadow Walk}</strong>&nbsp;Step into a shadowy realm to travel to a destination rapidly.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.t8QVxG4WCnd0a9QM]{Shrink Object}&nbsp;</strong>You shrink the target item, transmuting it into a smaller version of itself.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.SSEw9AIr2K5w5jlg]{Star Storm}&nbsp;</strong>Hailing plasma deals 6d8 electricity damage and 6d8 fire damage to creatures and objects in the area.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.IoR7MUe920ta3DzM]{Subjective Reality}</strong>&nbsp;You convince yourself one creature or object is an illusion.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.rJ0acpj21GDJYaim]{Summon Creature}&nbsp;</strong>This spell summons an extraplanar creature.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.rJqk12KW4phqFpI5]{Summon Drift Beacons}&nbsp;</strong>You conjure several Drift beacons into your current star system.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.ZklixLgh1xeuUEGz]{Terraform}</strong> Alter terrain and climate.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.VvCP8MdSZtXREp2x]{True Seeing}</strong>&nbsp;Target can see things as they really are.</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.1YyZmasD6hTQuBai]{Unspeakable Presences}</strong>&nbsp;Enemies in the area take 4d6 damage per round, cannot move, and might be devoured whole.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.SNdyYdSKnJmVE0B5]{Usher Apocalypse}</strong>&nbsp;Deal fire damage, create difficult terrain, and potentially anchor foes to the ground in the area.</span></p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.7EISvaUKg4YVj6RR]{Veil}</strong> Change appearance of a group of creatures.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.mtTo68t65tIfh8aG]{Wall of Steel}</strong>&nbsp;Wall has 45 Hit Points per inch of thickness and hardness 15.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>No Level</h2>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.gELZm5UXjjM3Bn1V]{Warp Reality}</strong>&nbsp;Alter reality to better suit you.</span></p>","flags":{},"folder":"","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","permission":{"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3,"default":0}}
{"_id":"CsrOFlvFJB0zY3Vb","name":"Settlement Qualities","content":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&gt; @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.TN4VeY75Z2Ce8IT7]{Settlements}</p>\n<table style=\"height: 338px; width: 99.1549%; float: left;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"8\" cellpadding=\"8\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Name</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; height: 18px;\">Source</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">Details</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 36px;\">Academic</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 36px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 36px;\">\n<p>&nbsp;It is often easier to do research in this settlement, which is home to a large school, research facility, or great repository of knowledge.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%;\">Automated</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center;\">AP #5 pg. 46</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%;\">\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">The majority of the city&rsquo;s civic functions (construction, maintenance, and so on) are performed by robots.</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%;\">Biotech-focused</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center;\">AP #5 pg. 49</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%;\">\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">The settlement relies less on devices that can be hacked or short-circuited, but it is more susceptible to @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.GnEF27Oot3zqTaBQ]{Diseases} and toxins.</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Bureaucratic</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">\n<p>&nbsp;The settlement is a nightmarish, confusing, and frustrating maze of red tape and official paperwork.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Cultured</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">\n<p>&nbsp;The settlement is well known for being a place where artistry thrives, such as a community of actors and musicians.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Devout</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">&nbsp;The settlement is devoted to a deity (which must be of the same alignment as the community) or follows a religious creed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 36px;\">Financial Center</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 36px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 36px;\">\n<p>&nbsp;This settlement is home to large banks, trading houses, currency exchanges and other powerful financial and mercantile organizations.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 50px;\">In Recession</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 50px;\">PW pg. 53</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 50px;\">\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">The settlement is experiencing an economic downturn, usually resulting in higher unemployment rates.</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Insular</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">\n<p>&nbsp;The settlement is isolated, perhaps physically. Its citizens are fiercely loyal to one another, often making it difficult to learn secrets about them.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Notorious</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">\n<p>&nbsp;The settlement has a reputation (deserved or not) for being a den of iniquity. It is usually easier to procure illegal goods and services.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%;\">Mobile</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center;\">AP #5 pg. 53</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%;\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">The settlement is not fixed at a single geographic location; it is difficult to map, and teleportation to the settlement is not possible without line of sight.</span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%;\">Modular</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center;\">PW pg.125</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%;\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">The compartmentalized nature of this settlement&rsquo;s construction allows for relatively easy and quick additions, renovations, and even physical rearrangement. It can also be used to physically separate parts of the city for quarantine or security purposes.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Polluted</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">&nbsp;The settlement&rsquo;s magical or high-tech industry has filled the ground and sky with disgusting pollution.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Profiteering</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">PW pg. 53</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">The businesses of this settlement engage in unethical practices in order to make profits.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%;\">Remote</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center;\">AP #4 pg. 50</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%;\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">Reaching this settlement is very difficult, often requiring secret knowledge or very specialized skills.</span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%;\">Surrounded By The Past</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center;\">AP #4 pg. 38</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%;\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">The citizens of the settlement live among the vestiges of their distant ancestors, though they can&rsquo;t usually take full advantage of such relics.</span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Technologically Advanced</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">&nbsp;The settlement produces and uses a level of technology that isn&rsquo;t widely seen elsewhere.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 18px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 18px;\">Technologically Average</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 18px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 18px;\">&nbsp;The level of technology used by the settlement is similar to that found in the majority of other settlements.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 4.72779%; height: 36px;\">Technologically Underdeveloped</td>\n<td style=\"width: 5.03981%; text-align: center; height: 36px;\">CRB pg. 405</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.1996%; height: 36px;\">&nbsp;The technology used by the settlement is less advanced than that found elsewhere.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"ET6OHjrdw8tykixd","name":"Sniper Weapons List","content":"<table style=\"border-color: #95A5A6; border-style: groove;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"4\" cellpadding=\"2\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 139px;\"><strong>Two-Handed Weapons</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 35px;\"><strong>Level</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\"><strong>Price</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\"><strong>Damage</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 41px;\"><strong>Range</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 48px;\"><strong>Critical</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 55px;\"><strong>Capacity</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 40px;\"><strong>Usage</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 31px;\"><strong>Bulk</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 174px;\"><strong>Special</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"background-color: #34495e; color: #ffffff;\">\n<td style=\"width: 694px;\" colspan=\"10\"><strong>Projectile</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 139px;\">@Compendium[sfrpg.equipment.G3jkh3c6tgshDEcl]{Shirren-Eye Rifle, Tactical}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">755</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">1d10 P</td>\n<td style=\"width: 41px;\">70 ft.</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48px;\">&mdash;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 55px;\">1 round</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 174px;\">Analog, sniper (250 ft.), unwieldy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: #c2e0f4;\">\n<td style=\"width: 139px;\">@Compendium[sfrpg.equipment.xY4MryhD3NCKQuC0]{Shirren-Eye Rifle, Advanced}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35px;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">9,350</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">2d10 P</td>\n<td style=\"width: 41px;\">70 ft.</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48px;\">&mdash;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 55px;\">4 rounds</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 174px;\">Analog, sniper (500 ft.), unwieldy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 139px;\">@Compendium[sfrpg.equipment.mt3jQbJ5QzFAMPzw]{Shirren-Eye Rifle, Elite}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35px;\">13</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">54,000</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">4d10 P</td>\n<td style=\"width: 41px;\">80 ft.</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48px;\">&mdash;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 55px;\">6 rounds</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 174px;\">Analog, sniper (750 ft.), unwieldy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: #c2e0f4;\">\n<td style=\"width: 139px;\">@Compendium[sfrpg.equipment.4pEGJmSlE7dcZiNM]{Shirren-Eye Rifle, Paragon}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35px;\">16</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">147,200</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">6d10 P</td>\n<td style=\"width: 41px;\">80 ft.</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48px;\">&mdash;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 55px;\">6 rounds</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 174px;\">Analog, sniper (1,000 ft.), unwieldy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 139px;\">@Compendium[sfrpg.equipment.tRPX0Xte8ULW9J6o]{Shirren-Eye Rifle, Warpshot}</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35px;\">20</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">740,800</td>\n<td style=\"width: 52px;\">10d10 P</td>\n<td style=\"width: 41px;\">80 ft.</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48px;\">&mdash;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 55px;\">4 rounds</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 174px;\">Analog, sniper (1,000 ft.), unwieldy</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","flags":{},"folder":"","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","permission":{"EgDbkW0aYa1c3C2f":3,"default":0}}
{"_id":"FOAXKvY33y1NVOPS","name":"Technomancer - Spells list","content":"<div class=\"content note-editor notes\">\n<h2>0-Level</h2>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.rSWg5JnN3mxzkatD]{Dancing Lights}</strong> Create and direct up to four lights.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.cmD9XPyg0Cud1xYO]{Daze}</strong> Humanoid creature of CR 3 or lower is @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.2XWEujYSyryB4oHm]{Dazed}.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.gEPdddzbgRAAa6j3]{Detect Affliction}</strong> Determine whether a creature or object has been poisoned, is diseased, is cursed, or is suffering a similar affliction.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.kxx5x0JAgFuEQJAm]{Detect Magic}</strong> Detect spells and magic items within 60 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.xNs98gJ8XLhmVyR3]{Energy Ray}</strong> Ray deals 1d3 acid, cold, electricity, or fire damage.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.mokTvzXcvubYC8tz]{Fabricate Scrap}&nbsp;</strong>Turn 1 bulk of inert matter into an equal amount of junked electronic equipment, suitable for certain spells.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.J1k3B5PmIc4SUC9L]{Ghost Sound}</strong> Create minor illusory sounds.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.QAU3felak3Etp6t1]{Mending}</strong> Restore 1d4 Hit Points to an object or construct.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.byAI5MUa3DgiiXc9]{Psychokinetic Hand}</strong> Telekinetically move an object of 1 bulk or less.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.R6MvvYVPDf21fE8Y]{Telepathic Message}</strong> Send a short telepathic message and hear simple telepathic replies.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.kNURbWD9d5768exU]{Token Spell}</strong> Perform simple magical effects.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.9oCAryPrAl3syg28]{Transfer Charge}</strong> Move charges from one power source to another source of the same type.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>1st-Level</h2>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.xQJexGLmCYF7VTdw]{Akashic Download} </strong>You do a cosmic search of the Akashic Record for information about a topic.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.kzOemsOWuqgbbGZw]{Baleful Polymorph} </strong>Change the target's shape to that of a smaller, weaker creature.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.zxecXzHipD4MEoFc]{Comprehend Languages}</strong> You understand all spoken, signed, and written or tactile languages.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.EYHidioFop7ygDoW]{Create Ammunition}&nbsp;</strong>Create a specific type of ammunition, such as arrows or a battery.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.uk49OnFMhCg9CSv1]{Detect Radiation}</strong> Detect radiation within 120 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>Detect Tech:</strong> Detect technological items with charges or that replenish charges within 60 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.HGg3fIQGDzUwueVa]{Disguise Self}</strong> Change your appearance.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.cOz93scOEdNFObSm]{Erase}</strong> Remove writings of either magical or mundane nature.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.3MJvj8HOhmqsq2pj]{Flight}</strong> One creature or object per level falls slowly.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.AInneaaTOM6vd3a7]{Gloom Mote}&nbsp;</strong>Create a mote of light from the Shadow Plane, which draws other nearby lights down into shadow.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.xPgI0T3aaPQnHE2Y]{Grease}</strong> Make a 10-ft. square or one object slippery.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.zf3yZsNXQTwa6vBD]{Hide Weapon}</strong> Hide a single operative weapon in your hand.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.XeeMyCERluyRvjOt]{Hold Portal}</strong> Hold a door shut.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.kDFNOMx78KU1GGol]{Holographic Image}</strong> Create a silent hologram of your design.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.PlIKBubNljqxVPsz]{Identify}</strong> Gain +10 bonus to identify items of a magic or technological nature.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.3yVTzdZy7GIxtk4h]{Incompetence}&nbsp;</strong>Targeted creatures lose proficiency with one type of weapons</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.yFhvmdW0BnMHV3Sm]{Jolting Surge}</strong> Touch deals 4d6 electricity damage.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.eemr4YD0xuzF67Zq]{Junk Armor}&nbsp;</strong>Turn junk into light armor or upgrade light armor to heavy armor</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.VI3PTc7yoywykyl3]{Junk Shards}&nbsp;</strong>You summon sharp fragments of technological junk that fly toward your target and deal 3d6 piercing and slashing damage.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.T4uX647wYIcHS8rj]{Junk Sword}&nbsp;</strong>Turn junk into a one-handed melee weapon</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.WVlj6EuKGCrjozBH]{Keen Senses}</strong> Target gains low-light vision and a +2 bonus to Perception checks.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.RtAXTXOSfg8YXiVA]{Know Coordinates}&nbsp;</strong>Briefly conjure a cybernetic augmentation.Learn the exact location of one creature on the same world as you.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.2l5Xk1YMzp0hlUok]{Life Bubble}</strong> Encase targeted creatures with a shell of tolerable atmosphere.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.jvJfulZZMmoO3gDs]{Lifting Frame}&nbsp;</strong>Holographic lifting frame increases the target&rsquo;s Strength modifier for carrying capacity and destroying objects.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.jUTs9R52bL7SuHwY]{Magic Missile}</strong> Two missiles deal 1d4+1 force damage.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.BrRuThVTv1aNfUKH]{Mental Silence}&nbsp;</strong>You create an anti-telepathic field around yourself.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.mNHdfIKpF11fhEjo]{Necromantic Revitalization}&nbsp;</strong>Restore hit points to an undead creature</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.a2zXJ84rzkD8SIBe]{Overheat}</strong> Deal 2d8 fire damage to creatures in cone.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.lsYASD3yhJfe8kwL]{Patch Tech}